fools ' parade is a 1971 american comedy film directed by andrew v. mclaglen and written by harry sauber . the film stars edmund lowe , lloyd nolan , and betty furness . the film was released on december 17 , 1971 , by metro-goldwyn-mayer . fools ' parade was released in the united states as fools ' parade ' parade . fools ' parade was released on december 17 , 1971 , by paramount pictures .